Previous EXPOs





Engineering EXPO at the University of South Florida has been bringing together the USF College of Engineering, the Tampa Bay community, and children since 1973. Beginning as a recruiting event for prospective students, it has grown into a showcase event meant to educate on STEM opportunities. Here are our most recent themes and logos.
